1. Install the latest stable installer of WinFSP from "https://github.com/billziss-gh/winfsp/releases".
2. Install the latest stable installer of SSHFS-Win from "https://github.com/billziss-gh/sshfs-win/releases".
3. Open File Explorer, right-click on This PC and choose Map network drive. 
   Choose a drive to mount at and in the Folder field enter: \\sshfs\yourRemoteLogin@ipv4xxx
   

在windows里运行的Python code可以使用对应的盘符访问该目录.  >>> 直接拖拽传输文件的速度要快于git里自带的scp
